@* _MoxfieldBulkEditHint *@
<details class="moxfield-bulkedit-hint">
    <summary>Want your Moxfield tags and categories to come through? Use Bulk Edit &rarr;</summary>
    <div class="moxfield-bulkedit-hint__body">
        <p>Moxfield's Bulk Edit view lists every card with its <code>#tags</code> inline — copy it, paste it into the text field here, and the tags travel with the deck. No extension required.</p>
        <ol class="moxfield-bulkedit-hint__steps">
            <li><strong>Open your deck</strong> on <a href="https://www.moxfield.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">moxfield.com</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>Click Bulk Edit.</strong> The <em>Main Deck</em> tab opens by default, with each card formatted like <code>1 Card Name (set) cn #Tag #Other</code>.</li>
            <li><strong>Copy the Main Deck contents</strong> and paste them into the text field here. Submit — tags are preserved end-to-end.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</details>
